{
  "title": "Magical Monsoon Spanish Shrimp Tapas Platter",
  "description": "A resinous and glassy jelly monsoon Spanish dish featuring yuzu kosho, fried to perfection, and packed with anti inflammatory friendly ingredients, served as a tapas platter.",
  "cuisine": "Spanish",
  "diet": [
